ing]]\" \n|-\n| 2009 || ''[[Mental (TV series)|Mental]]'' || Conor Stephens || Episode: \"[[Mental (TV series)#ep4|Manic at the Disco]]\"\n|-\n| 2009 || ''[[Hawthorne (TV series)|Hawthorne]]'' || Sam || Episode: \"[[Hawthorne (season 1)#ep3|Yielding]]\"\n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Ghost Whisperer]]'' || Pete Murphy || Episode: \"[[The Children's Parade]]\"\n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Sonny with a Chance]]'' || Wesley || Episode: \"[[Sonny with a Chance (season 2)#ep40|Sonny With a 100% Chance of Meddling]]\"\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[No Ordinary Family]]'' || Troy Cotten || Episode: \"[[No Ordinary Family#ep11|No Ordinary Friends]]\"\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Fish Hooks]]'' || Bradley \"Brad\" Kingstone || Voice role; 2 episodes\n|-\n| 2012\u20132016 || ''[[Lab Rats (U.S. TV series)|Lab Rats]]'' || Chase Davenport || Main role; 90 episodes\n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[Kickin' It]]'' || Brody || Episode: \"[[List of Kickin' It episodes#ep20|The Wrath of Swan]]\"\n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[A.N.T. Farm]]'' || Neville || Episode: \"[[List of A.N.T. Farm episodes#ep32|endurANTs]]\"\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Lab Rats: Elite Force]]'' || Chase || Credited as William Brent\n|}\n\n===Video games===\n{| class=wikitable\n|-\n! Year !! Title !! Voice role !! Notes\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Uncharted 3: Drake's Deception]]'' || Teenager [[Nathan Drake (character)|Nathan Drake]] || Also motion capture\n|-\n| 2012 || ''Skylanders: Giants'' || Commercial ||\n|-\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- \n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Role\n! Result\n! Refs\n|-\n| 2009\n| [[Young Artist Award]]\n| Best Performance in a DVD Film\n| Robby North in ''Cop Dog''\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"30thYAA\">{{cite web|url=http://www.youngartistawards.org/noms30.html|title=30th Annual Young Artist Awards|accessdate=May 11, 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2009\n| [[Young Artist Award]]\n| Best Performance in a TV Series \u2013 Guest Starring Young Actor\n| Teddy Carmichael in ''[[Medium (TV series)|Medium]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|